short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your web data extraction. Neferdata Extractor offers streamlined information retrieval in structured formats.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: With Neferdata extension you can leverage AI and Large Language Models to extract data from any website.
